#Conditionals and Loops


#Check number

#Given an integer n, find if n is positive, negative or 0. If n is positive, print "Positive"If n is negative, print "Negative",And if n is equal to 0, print "Zero".
#solution
n = int(input())
if n>0:
    print("Positive")
elif n<0:
    print("Negative")
elif n==0:
    print("Zero")
    
